{"tid":2414501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"的士司機總會總幹事等3人  IT 界建制派種票罪成","createTime":"2021-02-19T12:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T13:16:54.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"63d0748e8895aeaabee9da1322c8a6969c4a8b42","tid":2414501,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:32:46.000Z","msg":"2016 年立法會資訊科技界選舉疑出現賄選及種票，的士司機從業員總會（的總）幹事李林昌等 3 人，被控接受或向他人提供<span class=\"red\"> 1,000 元</span>，誘使投票予功能組別資訊科技界參選人、獲建制派支持的楊全盛，3 人今（19 日）在西九龍裁判法院裁決。三人供稱以不同原因加入有 IT 界選民資格的協會，被裁判官黃雅茵斥這說法荒謬及是謊言，他們的入會表格更有相同錯字，不可能如此湊巧，裁定所有罪名成立，案件押後至 3 月 5 日求情及判刑，期間被告以原有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告李林昌（47 歲，的總幹事）、陳俊成（60 歲，司機及的總會員）及其女兒陳曉彤（31 歲，接待員），三人同被控一項「串謀在選舉中作出舞弊行為提供利益予他人」罪。"},{"pid":"c9a01d8e925d7bd4d47d9e199cf9889bb4301564","tid":2414501,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%9A%84%E7%B8%BD%E5%B9%B9%E4%BA%8B%E7%AD%89-3-%E4%BA%BA-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83-it-%E7%95%8C%E7%A8%AE%E7%A5%A8%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E8%AA%98%E4%BD%BF%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E4%BA%88%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E8%BE%AF%E8%A7%A3%E8%8D%92%E8%AC%AC-%E5%A6%82%E8%AC%8A%E8%A8%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E5%25B9%25B9%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25AD%2589-3-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583-it-%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25AA%2598%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E4%25BA%2588%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%258D%2592%25E8%25AC%25AC-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%25AC%258A%25E8%25A8%2580%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGvtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=71f6a895\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnew